params._fhe_pk: The public key of the user

send_fhe_tx(string,string,string).details: Sends a transaction to the fhe_account

params._fhe_proof: The proof of the transaction (generated by the user's node and verified by the fhe_node)
params._fhe_tx_receiver: The receiver_fhe_tx of the transaction (generated by the user's node)
params._fhe_tx_sender: The sender_fhe_tx of the transaction  (generated by the user's node)

withdraw_ETH_request(uint256,string,stri.details: Transfers the ETH from the fhe_account to the msg.sender

params._amount: The amount of ETH to be withdrawn. This needs to be equal to the tokens owner in the fhe_account with _sk as the secret key
params._fhe_new_balance: The new balance of the user in the fhe_account
params._fhe_sk: The secret key used to encrypt the new public key
params._new_fhe_pk: The new public key to be used for future transactions
